Package polyhedra

Class Composite

  • java.lang.Object
    • polyhedra.Composite
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<Polyhedron>, Polyhedron
    public class Composite
extends java.lang.Object
implements Polyhedron, java.lang.Iterable<Polyhedron>
    A Composite Polyhedron. Polyhedra of this type are built from other Polyhedra. This,in theory, can include Composite objects composed of other (nested) Composite objects.
